author: Solus Prime
title: Nintendo franchises
text: == Games which generally Nintendo developed or co-developed, but the trademarks from the franchise belong to another company. This means that some part of the content belongs to Nintendo, as the case of music from GB ''Tetris'', or even characters such as Dr. Wright from ''SimCity''. Both of these examples reappear in the ''Super Smash Bros.'' series, which means that Nintendo considers this part of content from it creations.
